  "title": "Food Trade Company OFFICE CLERK",
  "description": "<p>1. \tCustomer Communication & Order Processing</p><p>• \tAnswer incoming calls and issue invoices based on customer orders.</p><p>• \tMaintain efficient and professional communication with customers.</p><p>• \tPromote company products through phone calls or text messages.</p><p>• \tHandle after‑sales customer service and coordinate with various internal departments.</p><p>• \tAssist with stock checking when required.</p><p>2. \tDocumentation & Administrative Support</p><p>• \tOrganize and archive documents to ensure proper record management.</p><p>• \tHandle daily administrative tasks such as checking emails, data entry, and updating records.</p><p>3. \tSkills Requirements</p><p>• \tProficient in common office software (e.g., Word, Excel).</p><p>• \tBasic English communication skills.</p><p>4. \tPersonal Qualities & Work Attitude</p><p>• \tAble to follow company arrangements and instructions.</p><p>• \tClear communication, cheerful personality, and quick thinking.</p><p>• \tResponsible, attentive, and patient.</p><p>• \tAble to work shifts when required.</p>",
